Reproduction . Schizogamous reproduction by gemmiparity behind chaetiger 26 (Cognetti's specimen) or chaetiger 30 . Stolon­bearing specimens found all year round, but mostly from Mars to May (
Cognetti 1957
).

Reproduction . Schizogamous reproduction by posterior scissiparity behind chaetiger 19, 22, 26 or 30 . Stolon­bearing specimens found from May to December (
Gidholm 1967
).
